1 virtually inspected; and
2 (iii) Except as provided in subdivision (b) of this subsection, the
3 virtual inspection is conducted live with both the individual requesting
4 or holding the building permit and the authorized inspector.
5 (b) Inspections required for building permits of a nonstructural
6 nature, as determined by the permitting entity, may be conducted using
7 video or photo documentation for any reinspection.
8 (3) Any state agency, county, city, or village that utilizes virtual
9 inspections shall not be required to publicize the list of personnel
10 provided in subdivision (2)(a) of this section.
11 Sec. 3. Original section 71-6401, Revised Statutes Cumulative
12 Supplement, 2024, is repealed.
